{"tid":743031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰開打，禁毒合作終止，中國繼續向美輸出鴉片類藥物","createTime":"2018-07-15T05:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T06:20:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95bcac40afe99332be0e57e679457b8bd5838aaf","tid":743031,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/201806240119china1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2F201806240119china1.jpg&h=6b70558c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國力圖遏止鴉片類藥物日益泛濫的努力，將在特朗普總統對中國發動貿易戰之後付諸東流。據《凱澤健康新聞》（Kaiser Health News）報道，美中貿易戰致使雙方一些與貿易無關的議題合作喊停，特別是針對芬太尼（fentanyl）等危險鴉片類藥物從中國輸入美國的問題。<br />\n<br />\n美國的大部分芬太尼和其他鴉片類藥物來自中國。芬太尼效力比海洛因強50倍，比嗎啡強100倍。據美國疾病控制及預防中心（CDC）的一份報告顯示，鴉片類藥物易已導致300萬美國人嗑藥上癮，去年6萬4千人死亡。雖然中國官員矢口否認向美國輸出鴉片類藥物，但過去曾努力與美國政府合作控制芬太尼向美國輸出。<br />\n<br />\n美國緝毒署（DEA）代理署長帕特森（Robert Patterson）於3月在國會發表一份聲明，將美國和中國緝毒機構之間的合作關係描述為：一個重要的雙邊機制，以解決非法芬太尼和其他合成藥物輸入美國。但緝毒署探員主任希金斯（Jeffrey Higgins）近日表示，美中貿易戰開打，已傳聞中國官員說：他們將不再與美國合作控制這些鴉片類藥物。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，如果特朗普繼續對中國加征關稅，美中的禁毒合作可能會完全終止，中國方面將放任鴉片類藥物繼續輸出美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180714-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E9%A1%9E%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20180714-%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2589%2593%25EF%25BC%258C%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%25B4%2589%25E7%2589%2587%25E9%25A1%259E%25E8%2597%25A5%25E7%2589%25A9&d=9HiKwmPHdzbrLPTrWo8NDC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d8b4f85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20180714-%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E9%96%8B%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E7%A6%81%E6%AF%92%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E5%90%91%E7%BE%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E9%B4%89%E7%89%87%E9%A1%9E%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9</a>"},{"pid":"c8af4f962c1b042691a2c394754a9f8be4cfe6e8","tid":743031,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T05:59:00.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦<br />\n遲d比人輸入返<br />\n又要打鴉片戰爭"},{"pid":"5d48043e69de5809d292c1a19cbd41eae4cef3fd","tid":743031,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"第三次鴉片戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17410210345eb5259dc23200d3e95f75b3c72e8","tid":743031,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"fentanyl 係癌症止痛藥?"},{"pid":"ff295cd0930826ef48476549e722a45e6f78bbca","tid":743031,"uid":85116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"依啲藥有得正常出入口?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f106259a4b0aea11751d3fe98622f413b78bc0a","tid":743031,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},{"pid":"c518d576f9f82914b41266807946864dea8a5c67","tid":743031,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f106259a4b0aea11751d3fe98622f413b78bc0a","tid":743031,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"中國又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim